"Big-Nosed Rare Species":
"I've just received word of a rare species sighting.
They're calling it a Dal Malre--a large native species
that inhabits the White Summit of Naberius. Despite
the eyewitness reports we've received, we know so
little about it that it's still shrouded in mystery. That's
why I would like you to go investigate at once. I'll
await your hopefully favorable response.

*Target: Dal Malres level 41 or higher"

"希少種の目撃情報が寄せられた。
大型の原生種、ダル・マルリ。
ナベリウスの凍土に生息するらしい。

目撃報告はあるものの、実情はまだまだ
謎に包まれ、未解明な部分が多い。
だからこそ、早く調査を行いたいのだ。
良い返事を期待しているよ。

※Lv.41以上のダル・マルリが対象"
